  "text": "We also made another comparison with mean Nusselt numbers for a triangular enclosure at E = 0 and AR = 1 including high Rayleigh numbers. The results are presented in Table 1 . The comparison of results showed that there is good agreement between present study and literature (Asan and Namli, [CITATION_1] ).",
